frames.caption: A powerful figure stands confidently on a rocky cliff overlooking the ocean at sunset. Clad in a striking red and gold armor, the character gazes into the distance, exuding strength and determination.
frames.description: The scene is set on a coastal cliff during sunset, with the ocean stretching out to the horizon. The warm glow of the setting sun casts a golden light over the scene, highlighting the character's elaborate armor.
